Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（空）朧～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}大丈夫か？
